    [Project7].[esGeneral] AS [esGeneral], 
    [Project7].[usuarioRegistroId] AS [usuarioRegistroId], 
    [Project7].[fechaRegistro] AS [fechaRegistro], 
    [Project7].[clave] AS [clave], 
    [Project7].[armarCobroMostrador] AS [armarCobroMostrador], 
    [Project7].[categoriaProductoId] AS [categoriaProductoId], 
    [Project7].[urlImagen] AS [urlImagen], 
    [Project7].[indice] AS [indice], 
    [Project7].[areaPreparacionId] AS [areaPreparacionId], 
    [Project7].[principal] AS [principal]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Distinct1].[descripcion] AS [descripcion], 
        1 AS [C1], 
        [Project6].[idProducto] AS [idProducto], 
        [Project6].[comercioId] AS [comercioId], 
        [Project6].[nombre] AS [nombre], 
        [Project6].[precio] AS [precio], 
        [Project6].[activo] AS [activo], 
        [Project6].[mermaPermitida] AS [mermaPermitida], 
        [Project6].[esCombo] AS [esCombo], 
        [Project6].[esGeneral] AS [esGeneral], 
        [Project6].[usuarioRegistroId] AS [usuarioRegistroId], 
        [Project6].[fechaRegistro] AS [fechaRegistro], 
        [Project6].[clave] AS [clave], 
        [Project6].[armarCobroMostrador] AS [armarCobroMostrador], 
        [Project6].[categoriaProductoId] AS [categoriaProductoId], 
        [Project6].[urlImagen] AS [urlImagen], 
        [Project6].[indice] AS [indice], 
        [Project6].[areaPreparacionId] AS [areaPreparacionId], 
        [Project6].[principal] AS [principal], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project6].[idProducto] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C2]
        FROM   (SELECT DISTINCT 
            [Extent2].[descripcion] AS [descripcion]
            FROM  [ads].[Productos] AS [Extent1]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [ads].[CategoriaProductos] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[categoriaProductoId] = [Extent2].[idCategoriaProducto]
            WHERE ([Extent1].[categoriaProductoId] IS NOT NULL) AND ( EXISTS (SELECT 
                1 AS [C1]
                FROM [dbo].[comercios] AS [Extent3]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[comercioId] = [Extent3].[idComercio]) AND ( EXISTS (SELECT 
                    1 AS [C1]
                    FROM [dbo].[confUsuarioComercio] AS [Extent4]
                    WHERE ([Extent3].[idComercio] = [Extent4].[comercioId]) AND ([Extent4].[usuarioId] = @p__linq__0)
                ))
            )) AND ([Extent1].[activo] = 1) ) AS [Distinct1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT 
            [Extent5].[idProducto] AS [idProducto], 
            [Extent5].[comercioId] AS [comercioId], 
            [Extent5].[nombre] AS [nombre], 
            [Extent5].[precio] AS [precio], 
            [Extent5].[activo] AS [activo], 
            [Extent5].[mermaPermitida] AS [mermaPermitida], 
            [Extent5].[esCombo] AS [esCombo], 
            [Extent5].[esGeneral] AS [esGeneral], 
            [Extent5].[usuarioRegistroId] AS [usuarioRegistroId], 
            [Extent5].[fechaRegistro] AS [fechaRegistro], 
            [Extent5].[clave] AS [clave], 
            [Extent5].[armarCobroMostrador] AS [armarCobroMostrador], 
            [Extent5].[categoriaProductoId] AS [categoriaProductoId], 
            [Extent5].[urlImagen] AS [urlImagen], 
            [Extent5].[indice] AS [indice], 
            [Extent5].[areaPreparacionId] AS [areaPreparacionId], 
            [Extent5].[principal] AS [principal], 
            [Extent6].[idCategoriaProducto] AS [idCategoriaProducto], 
            [Extent6].[descripcion] AS [descripcion]
            FROM  [ads].[Productos] AS [Extent5]
            LEFT OUTER JOIN [ads].[CategoriaProductos] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[categoriaProductoId] = [Extent6].[idCategoriaProducto]
            WHERE ([Extent5].[categoriaProductoId] IS NOT NULL) AND ( EXISTS (SELECT 
                1 AS [C1]
                FROM [dbo].[comercios] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE ([Extent5].[comercioId] = [Extent7].[idComercio]) AND ( EXISTS (SELECT 
                    1 AS [C1]
                    FROM [dbo].[confUsuarioComercio] AS [Extent8]
                    WHERE ([Extent7].[idComercio] = [Extent8].[comercioId]) AND ([Extent8].[usuarioId] = @p__linq__0)
                ))
            )) AND ([Extent5].[activo] = 1) ) AS [Project6] ON ([Distinct1].[descripcion] = [Project6].[descripcion]) OR (([Distinct1].[descripcion] IS NULL) AND ([Project6].[descripcion] IS NULL))
    )  AS [Project7]
    ORDER BY [Project7].[descripcion] ASC, [Project7].[C2] ASC

    [Extent1].[descripcion] AS [descripcion], 
     CAST( [Extent1].[idProveedor] AS nvarchar(max)) AS [C1], 
    CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[idProveedor] = @p__linq__1) THEN cast(1 as bit) WHEN ( NOT (([Extent1].[idProveedor] = @p__linq__1) AND (0 = (CASE WHEN (@p__linq__1 IS NULL) THEN cast(1 as bit) ELSE cast(0 as bit) END)))) THEN cast(0 as bit) END AS [C2]
    FROM [ads].[Proveedores] AS [Extent1]
    WHERE  EXISTS (SELECT
